msgid "Show button on bottom toolbar"
msgstr "在底部工具列顯示按鈕"

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:232
msgid ""
"Draw a profile directly in the sky: hold Shift and drag with the left mouse "
"button to add points; hold Shift and drag with the right mouse button to "
"erase nearby points."
msgstr "直接在天空中繪製輪廓：按住 Shift 並用左鍵拖曳新增點；按住 Shift 並用右鍵拖曳擦除附近的點。"

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:233
msgid "Start drawing profile"
msgstr "開始繪製輪廓"

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:234
msgid "Finish and save drawing"
msgstr "完成並儲存繪製"

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:235
msgid "Appearance"
msgstr "外觀"

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:236
msgid "Fill opacity:"
msgstr "填充透明度："

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:237
msgid "Line opacity:"
msgstr "線條透明度："

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:238
msgid "Line width:"
msgstr "線寬："

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:241
msgid "Save settings"
msgstr "儲存設定"

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:253
msgid "Version:"
msgstr "版本："

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:254
msgid "License:"
msgstr "授權條款："

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:255
msgid "Authors:"
msgstr "作者："

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:258
msgid ""
"Use an Az/Alt obstruction table to visualize buildings, trees, terrain, or "
"other local horizon blockers without replacing the active Stellarium "
"landscape."
msgstr ""
"使用方位角/高度角遮擋表來顯示建築、樹木、地形或其他本地地平線遮擋物，而不替換"
"目前 Stellarium 地景。"

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:259
msgid ""
"Wide-field rendering uses a shader mask when available and falls back to a "
"CPU screen mask when needed."
msgstr "大視場渲染會優先使用 shader 遮罩；不可用時會回退到 CPU 螢幕遮罩。"

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:290
msgid "Settings are saved automatically."
msgstr "設定會自動儲存。"

#: src/gui/HorizonOverlayDialog.cpp:317
msgid "Settings saved."
msgstr "設定已儲存。"
